      <notesStmt>
        <note>Title from incipit (f. 1r); alternate title Karkaṭīvratakathā from colophon (f. 9v).</note>
        <note>Written in 9-11 lines per leaf.</note>
        <note>9 leaves foliated 1-9, lower right verso.</note>
        <note>Mistakes blacked out; some corrections and additions in margins.</note>
        <note>Written on European paper with watermarks. The same scribe and paper were also used for Item 1447, Item 1453, Item 1455, Item 1456, and Item 1459, and may have originally been from the same manuscript as one or more of these items.</note>
